"O/D-A pricey buy but pretty tasty. I think carrying the same name as it's predecessor hurts it for me. I would like it better if I didn't know how good the base beer was. This is a downgrade from the normal Imperial Biscotti Break but it's still a cool brew to try."
""
"Overall- Good beer and solid. Slightly above average in comparison to many of the imperial stouts I've had. Worth at try but wait for it on tap. I would not splurge for the bottle."
